            <p><add hand="#barker">Order for a drawing knife.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p><placeName>Collorado </placeName><date when="1824-03-05">March 5th 1824</date></p>
<p>Dear Sir</p>

<p>I would take it as a singular favour if you will send Me one of
your Drawing knives By <persName>Mr. Beeson</persName> and I shall settle with you
the first time I come over</p>

<p><persName>Jn° Andrews</persName></p>
<p><persName>Mr. B Austin</persName></p>


        </div1>
